item.description:
Hi Everyone,

We are having a high intermediate to advance pick-up game this Sunday, March 3rd at 2:30pm at the Lawrence YMCA. This game is for Yankee C- and above level. Players should be familiar with how to play 6-2 and 5-1 formations.

Please message me to get on the roster. If you have not played in my meetups recently, please mention the level of your play and confirm that you can play formations. If your name is not on the roster, you are not guaranteed a spot to play.

The meetup is free and YMCA membership is not required. There is plenty of parking at the lot behind the building. When you enter, look for the big gym upstairs.

Best,

Katya
